        "setup": "Generate an App Key in the Refinitiv/LSEG App Key Generator at [App Key Generator](https://emea1-apps.platform.refinitiv.com/apps/appkeygenerator). Community guidance says this App Key is the `CLIENT_ID` for Refinitiv Data Platform access, and it should be created with the `EDP API` option enabled; use your permissioned human RDP user ID when generating it. See [How to create clientID (APIKey) for Refinitiv Data Platform](https://community.developers.refinitiv.com/discussion/90841/how-to-create-clientid-apikey-for-refinitiv-data-platform/p1) and [Getting auth token - how to fill request](https://community.developers.refinitiv.com/discussion/89163/getting-auth-token-how-to-fill-request/p1)."
